# Federated Learning + DQN (Healthcare)

Privacy-preserving Service Time prediction and Resource optimization.

## 🔮 FL Task
- **Service Time Prediction:** Global model for treatment duration per ESI level.

## 🤖 DQN Task
- **Resource Allocation:** Real-time staff/bed distribution across 5 ESI queues.

## Scalability
- **Opacus:** Differential Privacy.
- **FSDP:** Model sharding.
